{"tid":216134,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足同我一樣酒量麻麻?","createTime":"2017-04-25T02:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T03:02:30.000Z","uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"824693405d90facd5d84003f462a7819e2ff4e99","tid":216134,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:07:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日女朋友去左日本旅行 <br />\n所以屋企得番自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住尋晚，我沖完涼 <br />\n發覺電話有十幾個misscall <br />\n原來我朋友岩岩比男友飛左 <br />\n喊哂口咁同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後傾左成個鐘電話 <br />\n佢忽然話：不如出來陪我飲酒？ <br />\n但係個陣已經成十一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我見屋企無咩人 <br />\n又懶出去 <br />\n就話：不如你上來啦 我屋企又齊酒 <br />\n有私人空間又慳錢 <br />\n於是佢就上左來... <br />\n我地vodka,rum,啤酒,blue curacao, tequila <br />\n咩都溝下來飲 <br />\n結果唔使一個鐘兩個已經醉醉地同好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然 <br />\n佢對眼水汪汪咁問我： <br />\n你可唔可以 錫我一淡？ <br />\n可能真係能成為密友大概總帶著愛 <br />\n我竟然諗都無諗就錫左落去 <br />\n結果我地越咀越激 <br />\n互相纏住大家條頸 <br />\n舌頭交纏住咁行左入我房 <br />\n一攤上床 <br />\n我地互相摷左陣大家就埋牙 <br />\n詳細就唔多講 <br />\n只可以講係幾開心 <br />\n大家都出左兩次先攬住訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家覺得好對唔住女朋友 <br />\n同埋覺得同佢既友誼變左質 <br />\n巴絲你地話點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b5b5890e30378689fa33da801e723d6b69577b","tid":216134,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"🤦🏼&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"727a2c0f6778bd18d715a7658ab35d2ba332d334","tid":216134,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:17:05.000Z","msg":"樓主飲fruit punch都會醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66efaa388c8d5ab8623051bf85230424ebe793ef","tid":216134,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0